+ Usage

This is a theme page made for the [[[Decom. Dept. Hub|Decommissioning Department]]], created by [[*user Calibold]]

To import this theme to your page, put the following anywhere inside it:

> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:decom-dept]]@@

If you'd prefer a pride logo instead of the normal one, put this instead:

> @@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:decom-dept |inc-pride= --]]]@@

[[include component:image-block
| name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Adecom-dept/Decom.%20Dept.%20Logo.svg
| caption=This is an image block.
| width=200px]]

You can view any page's Backlinks by clicking "+ Options" at the bottom of the page, then "Backlinks".

